snippet.title: Tetris or treat! Playable pumpkin Tetris haunts Halloween
snippet.description: Forget candy. The coolest treat for Halloween this year is a playable pumpkin Tetris rigged with 128 LED lights.

snippet.title: Sony Action Cam HDR-AS30V
snippet.description: Joining the AS30V's new hardware features are a new waterproof housing and several accessories and mounts, bringing it closer to the competition.

snippet.title: Pinterest amps up recipe search with new filters
snippet.description: The social network adds dietary filters and the ability to search by ingredients.

snippet.title: Walmart buys recipe startup to pair with online grocery delivery
snippet.description: In its quest to tackle the online grocery delivery market and bulk up its Walmart To Go service, the retail giant snaps up the recipe-minded Yumprint.

snippet.title: Pumpkin cheesecake: the perfect treat
snippet.description: The Mini Pumpkin Cheesecake Pan can turn out a perfect fall dessert: miniature cheesecakes shaped like pumpkins.

snippet.title: Pinterest acquires recipe sharing Punchfork
snippet.description: The social site makes its first purchase, choosing the food recipe bookmarking network.

snippet.title: Contest: Carve a geeky pumpkin for Crave
snippet.description: With Halloween just a few weeks away, we invite our readers to participate in Crave's first techy pumpkin-carving contest.

snippet.title: Pie in the sky: Domino's delivers pizzas via octocopter
snippet.description: A Domino's UK publicity stunt shows what it would look like if pizzas were delivered by RC helicopters.

snippet.title: Nexus 5 rampages through benchmarks, has 'Key Lime Pie'
snippet.description: Google's next Nexus has popped up on benchmarking site GFXBench and absolutely killed it, outclassing many a famous mobile and shedding light on its specs.

snippet.title: What to expect from Android Key Lime Pie
snippet.description: Google should unveil a new version of its mobile OS next week. Here's some of what we may see this time around, and also down the line.
